properties.headline: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS - The Rocks Markets - THE ROCKS George St between Hickson Rd AND Lower Fort St
properties.otherAdvice:

Clearways will be in effect every weekend from 10pm Friday until 10pm Sunday on the eastern side of George St between Hickson Rd and Lower Fort St.

Clearways are strict no-parking zones and apply even to local residents or Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs before parking as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.

properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS Police operation - GOSFORD Donnison Street (Pacific Highway) between Dane Drive AND Mann Street
properties.publicTransport:
Due to a police operation on
Donnison Street, some services are delayed. As well, Route 55 and 70 buses
are diverting away from part of Donnison Street. Buses heading to Gosford are
using Dane Drive, Georgiana Terrace and Mann Street instead, missing two stops.
Buses heading away from Gosford are using Mann Street, Donnison Street, Henry
Parry Drive, Erina Street East, Mann Street, Racecourse Road and Showground
Road instead, missing one stop.
